<body>
<div>

    <b><span class="underline">Full Screen </span></b><br/>
Get a bigger screen for the app by removing the top notification bar.
<br/><br/>
  
    <b><span class="underline">Tutorial Mode </span></b><br/>
Turn on/off the messages that are displayed while entering data on any field.
<br/><br/>

	<b><span class="underline">Manage Lists</span></b><br/>
LOV stands for List of values
All the values in the fields that auto-complete can be added and deleted here.
<br/><br/>

	<b><span class="underline">Start Syncing</span></b><br/>
The app syncs all the records, voice and images when you are in the wi-fi zone but if you want to sync before that, you can click the start syncing button to sync data over the 3G network.
<br/><br/>

    <b><span class="underline">Sync Frequency</span></b><br/>
Adjust the behavior of your app to automatically sync as much as possible or to optimize network utilization.
<br/><br/>

	<b><span class="underline">Flash Always On</span></b><br/>
Will keep the flash always on when using the camera.
<br/><br/>

	<b><span class="underline">Resize images</span></b><br/>
will automatically resize images before transmitting to your cloud account.
<br/><br/>

	<b><span class="underline">Feedback</span></b><br/>
For questions and feedback please write to <a href="feedback@smarthumanoid.com">feedback@smarthumanoid.com</a>.
<br/><br/>

	
 
</div>
</body>
</html>